</span><span class='line'><span class="c">#&lt;/p&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>&lt;h1&gt;Function that starts the daemon/service&lt;/h1&gt;
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>&lt;p&gt;#
